e-btn']","popover":{"title":"Create a Template","description":"On the Templates tab, click New Template to save a reusable preset (name, content, default severity, default scope, and whether acknowledgment is required by default). Delete a template from its row's trash icon — that does not affect announcements already sent from it.","side":"left"}}]}"""
